transcripts.text: President Trump promised to protect the American worker.
This is our mantra, buy American and hire American.
But the corporate fat cats and Wall Street snakes don't want him to deliver on that promise.

I have saved you, cried the woman, and you've bitten me, heavens, why?  You know your bite is poisonous, and now I'm going to die.  Oh, shut up, silly woman, said the reptile with a grin.  You knew damn well I was a snake before you took me in.  Tell President Trump to keep the Koch brothers' cheap labor agenda out of the White House.
